<div id="review_2712277802" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2712277802" />
    <a title="☠Kayla☠" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/93439193-kayla"><img alt="☠Kayla☠" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1591895268p2/93439193.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2712277802?book_show_action=true">Aug 08, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="☠Kayla☠" class="user" itemprop="url" name="☠Kayla☠" href="/user/show/93439193-kayla">☠Kayla☠</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2712277802" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2663766578103408284">I absolutely love Mary Downing Hahn&apos;s stories! They have such a creepy and unsettling vibe to them that it makes it hard to believe that they are actually middle grade novels. She adds just enough detail for you to use you&apos;re imagination to fill in the rest and I love how her books are so short and very easy to read. They&apos;re great books for anyone who&apos;s looking for a spooky story and just wants to get in a quick read. This one in particular I really enjoyed! It was a bit slow to start out with b</span>
  <span id="freeText2663766578103408284" style="display:none">I absolutely love Mary Downing Hahn's stories! They have such a creepy and unsettling vibe to them that it makes it hard to believe that they are actually middle grade novels. She adds just enough detail for you to use you're imagination to fill in the rest and I love how her books are so short and very easy to read. They're great books for anyone who's looking for a spooky story and just wants to get in a quick read. This one in particular I really enjoyed! It was a bit slow to start out with but kept the creepy vibe through out it which was a huge plus for me. I personally like going into her books not really knowing to much of what they're about because it adds mystery to the creepiness. I'm very pleased that I went into this one not knowing a thing about it.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2663766578103408284" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

