<span id="freeTextContainer3301982409856079543">A blended family moves to the country. The host of characters includes a mother with two children, a father with a bratty little girl and her ghost friend Helen.<br/><br/>While the story was well crafted, I couldn&apos;t connect with it and cannot recommend it. It will go back to the library sale table tomorrow.</span>
